  "keyFeatures": [
    "One-liner installation on Debian, Ubuntu, and Raspberry Pi OS",
    "Web-based dashboard with hardware utilization widgets",
    "App store with one-click Docker app installation (100,000+ apps)",
    "Elegant file and drive manager with no technical knowledge required",
    "SMB/Samba network share management",
    "ZeroTier network integration for remote access",
    "WebSocket-based real-time hardware status updates",
    "REST API (v1 and v2) with JWT authentication",
    "Multi-architecture support: amd64, arm64, armv7",
    "SystemD service integration with automatic startup"
  ],
